{
  "clauseId": "3ee8856267324170a038b7de496b2986",
  "clauseName": "3.2.1_农产品精简版V3.0-new（20260414165344）",
  "clauseNumber": "3.2.1",
  "clauseContent": "3.2.1.  发票勾选\n在数电票试点后，农产品发票的进项抵扣必须先通过电子税务局进行“抵扣勾选”（税控票时期企业通过增值税发票综合服务平台勾选发票，目前仍在使用税控盘开具发票的企业极少，基本上都是通过电子税务局开具、勾选发票），不能直接填表。具体操作路径：\n<div class=\"quill-better-table-wrapper\"><table class=\"quill-better-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><colgroup><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-row=\"1\"><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">发票类型</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">操作路径</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">说明</strong></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"2\"><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"2\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">农产品销售发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">左上角带“自产农产品销售”标签的免税数电票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【抵扣勾选】→&nbsp;直接勾选</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">与常规专票操作相同。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"3\"><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">税控系统开具的自产农产品免税发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【待处理农产品发票】→【自产农产品销售发票】→&nbsp;处理&nbsp;→&nbsp;再回到【抵扣勾选】</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">需先预处理，确认是否为自产。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"4\"><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">小规模纳税人开具的3%农产品专票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【待处理农产品发票】→【从小规模处购进的3%农产品专票】→&nbsp;处理（选择“按票面金额和基础扣除率”）→&nbsp;再回到【抵扣勾选】</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">预处理时需选择抵扣方式：</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">①按票面金额×9%计算抵扣（推荐）</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">②按票面税额抵扣（不推荐）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"5\"><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">税务机关代开的农产品免税发票（个人自产）</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【抵扣勾选】→【代开农产品发票录入】→&nbsp;补录信息&nbsp;→&nbsp;再回到【抵扣勾选】</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">补录销售方信息、发票代码、号码、金额等。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"6\"><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">农产品收购发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【抵扣勾选】→&nbsp;直接勾选</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">由购买方自行开具，系统可识别。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"7\"><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1%农产品专票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【抵扣勾选】→&nbsp;直接勾选</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面税额抵扣，无需特殊处理。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
